headline: News Corp Announces Match for U.S. Government’s $1,000 Contribution to Children’s Investment Accounts
summary: NEW YORK, February 19, 2026--News Corporation (NASDAQ: NWSA, NWS; ASX: NWS, NWSLV) announced today that it will match the U.S. government’s one-time $1,000 contribution to the Section 530A accounts ("Trump Accounts") designed to "jumpstart the American Dream" for children across the country.
